title: Maninang Kristo maharini fwrwngiri
lyrics:
Maninang Kristo maharini fwrwngiri
Sofwinw hanai be khwmsaliao -2
Gaoba gaoni besen gwsa somkhow
Jrab gargarnanwi nuja fwibai dinwi be thiliao -2
(a)
Ma lananwi jwnglai somai hwnw
Ma hwnanwi jwnglai gwjwn hwnw -2
Gwsw gwrbwni khulumnaikhou najaodw
Sarsrwnan hwlangdw bwrni jhwri -2
(b)
Dihunnan hw jwngnw mwnse raha
Thulunga hw jwngnw gosongtanw -2
Phwthainayao jwngkhow fwgwmnanwi galangdw
Lukhanglangdw jwngkhow O guru -2
